1. Andrea je otišla u prodavnicu da kupi hleb i mleko. (*Andrea*, She went to the store to buy bread and milk.) 
2. Da li si video *Andreinu* novu frizuru? (Have you seen *Andrea's* new hairstyle?)
3. *Andrein* telefon je zvonio, ali nije bila u mogućnosti da se javi. (*Andrea's* phone was ringing, but she wasn't able to answer.)
4. *Andreo*, da li želiš da idemo na piće večeras? (*Andrea*, do you want to go for a drink tonight?)
5. Imaš li nešto zajedničko sa *Andreom* osim prezimena? (Do you have anything in common with *Andrea* besides your last name?)
6. *Andrea* je veoma kreativna osoba, voli da slika i piše pesme. (*Andrea* is a very creative person, she likes to paint and write songs.)
7. Ovaj film mi se ne sviđa, ali *Andreinom* bratu se dopada. (I don't like this movie, but *Andrea's* brother likes it.)
8. *Andreina* mama je juče bila na operaciji, ali sada se dobro oseća. (*Andrea's* mom had surgery yesterday, but she's feeling well now.)
9. Molim te, pozovi *Andreu* i reci joj da je sastanak u petak. (Please call *Andrea* and tell her that the meeting is on Friday.)
10. *Andrea* je već stigla u kancelariju, čekamo samo ostale kolege. (*Andrea* has already arrived at the office, we're just waiting for the other colleagues.)